ygData.subject: Hello all
ygData.msgSnippet: Hi Everyone, I just found this group and believe me, I ve been looking for it for a long time! I had been on every search engine I could think of and nothing
ygData.messageBody:
Hi Everyone,

I just found this group and believe me, I've been looking for it for
a long time! I had been on every search engine I could think of and
nothing was coming up, finally I got to HOTBOT and there it was
EQ_Rainbow. As I was clicking the link, I thought for sure it would
be dead. But it wasn't (YAY!) and here I am. I always knew there had
to be others on EQ, but I was starting to have doubts.

I have been playing on Morrel-Thule for the last 7 months or so, but
not reguarly until recently. Anyway, I have decided that since I
finally found the group, I am going to move over to Rodcet Nife and
create a new character (I can't believe I have to be a newbie AGAIN!)
At least, no one took my name. :-)

Anyway, I just wanted to say "Hey" to everyone and if you are in EQ
on Rodcet Nife give a /tell to Kedek, I am very interested in joining
the guild.

Until then,

Kedek Vega
2nd season Rodcet Nife
Barbarian-Shaman
